overview:
AboutEyes.co.uk a young dynamic company, dedicated to providing top quality reading glasses, reading sunglasses, sunglasses AND service.

We are well established, with a reputation for providing distinctive, design-led fashion readers at competitive prices.

We change our collection of readers and sunreaders frequently to ensure that our customers have always something new and interesting to see and purchase.

We believe that customer service is pivotal to the success of our company.

Your order will be processed quickly and efficiently and our friendly customer service team will be happy to discuss and advise you on any point you might have about our reading glasses, sunreaders, bifocal sunreaders or sunglasses.
